    [
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1 H3C LA2608 室内无线网关用户手册"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                61,
                613,
                85
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.1 概述"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                102,
                196,
                123
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "H3C LA2608-GM/GU 室内无线网关（以下简称 LA2608）可以为用户提供无线服务，为了实现对设备的管理，LA2608需要通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                139,
                138,
                905,
                176
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/16288d553bf867b279adb856534213ef37a0d17bdec59c9c4abf824878cd7e56.jpg"
                },
                "content": "",
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                188,
                186,
                213
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "说明"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                188,
                197,
                226,
                214
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "目前，LA2608只支持与 H3C公司的无线控制器互通。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                224,
                564,
                241
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.2 配置LA2608与无线控制器互通"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                282,
                484,
                302
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "如 图 1 所示，LA2608 安装了SIM卡，通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器，并向用户提供无线服务。关于LA2608的安装方法，请参见“H3C LA2608室内无线网关 快速安装指南”。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                139,
                320,
                905,
                356
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "图1 配置 LA2608与无线控制器互通"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                362,
                431,
                378
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/2436b496658837dfc940d48d8565fa9a9135932ebf6e2c2a25e9fff4f674dd39.jpg"
                },
                "content": "",
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                147,
                391,
                806,
                581
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.2.1 配置LA2608"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                625,
                263,
                644
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(1) 配置拨号访问组的拨号控制列表"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                659,
                438,
                676
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "<LA2608>system-view\n[LA2608]dialer-rule 1 ip permit\n(2) 配置 DCC 拨号"
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                682,
                416,
                733
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/06474f326a73aa174281952c2d7a262f50b5a813a0a0523744c4cc52374ef0fd.jpg"
                },
                "content": "",
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                747,
                188,
                771
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "dialer number命令用来配置发起呼叫的拨号串，不同运营商的拨号串不同，请用户在配置前向网络运营商获取发起呼叫的拨号串。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                141,
                781,
                905,
                817
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608]interface Cellular-Ethernet2/0\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]ip address cellular-allocated\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer enable-circular\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer-group 1\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer idle 0"
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "powershell"
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                849,
                647,
                931
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_number",
            "content": {
                "page_number_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                504,
                948,
                515,
                960
            ]
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer autodial 5\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer number *99# autodial\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]nat outbound\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]quit\n\n(3) 配置 DNS 解析功能\n[LA2608]dns resolve\n\n(4) 配置静态路由\n[LA2608]ip route-static 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 Cellular-Ethernet2/0\n\n(5) 指定运营商无线控制器的 IP 地址\n[LA2608] wlan ac ip 60.191.99.143"
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                49,
                665,
                238
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.2.2 配置运营商无线控制器"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                92,
                249,
                352,
                267
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/08e8c1c7f9c7f47a615d8449dea68240baed840efe2f63d2a292dceb249bef98.jpg"
                },
                "content": "",
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                289,
                188,
                314
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "说明"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                189,
                298,
                226,
                314
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "如下配置仅供参考，运营商可根据实际情况进行调整。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                324,
                561,
                340
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(1) 创建业务 VLAN"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 2
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                374,
                312,
                391
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(1) 创建业务 VLAN\n<AC>system-view\n[AC]vlan 2\n[AC-vlan2] quit\n(2) 创建 WLAN-ESS 接口并加入业务 VLAN\n[AC]interface WLAN-ESS 1\n[AC-WLAN-ESS1]port access vlan 2\n[AC-WLAN-ESS1]quit\n(3) 配置明文方式的服务模板\n[AC]wlan service-template 1 clear\n[AC-wlan-st-1]ssid ssidh3c\n[AC-wlan-st-1]bind WLAN-ESS 1\n[AC-wlan-st-1]service-template enable\nPlease wait... Done.\n[AC-wlan-st-1]quit\n(4) 开启自动 AP 功能\n[AC]wlan auto-ap enable\n[AC]wlan ap 2608 model LA2608 id 1\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]serial-id auto\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]radio 1\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]service-template 1\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]radio enable\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]quit\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]quit\n(5) 配置 VLAN 接口 IP 地址\n[AC]interface Vlan-interface 1\n[AC-Vlan-interface1]ip address 60.191.99.143 255.255.0.0\n[AC-Vlan-interface1]quit\n[AC]interface Vlan-interface 2\n[AC-Vlan-interface2]ip address 10.249.136.1 255.255.252.0\n[AC-Vlan-interface2]quit\n(6) 使能 DHCP 服务，配置 DHCP 地址池"
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                378,
                638,
                941
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_number",
            "content": {
                "page_number_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "2"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                504,
                948,
                517,
                959
            ]
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[AC]dhcp enable\n[AC]dhcp server ip-pool vlan2\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]network 10.249.136.0 22\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]gateway-list 10.249.136.1\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]dns-list 218.201.96.130\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]quit"
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
